  "instructions": [
    "Steam the soybeans until tender. Chop the onions and garlic finely.",
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat. Add chopped onions and cook until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic to the pan and sauté for another minute.",
    "Stir in soy sauce, vinegar, sesame seeds, salt, and cooked soybeans. Simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Garnish with finely chopped tomatoes and chili peppers just before serving."
